borrowDebt(uint256,uint256,uint32,uint12.details: Calculates shares, checks liquidity, and handles cross-chain or local transfers. Accrues interest before borrowing.

params._amount: The amount of tokens to borrow.
params._chainId: The chain id of the destination network.

params.borrower: The address of the borrower to check

returns.borrowValue: The current borrow value in USD
returns.collateralValue: The current collateral value in USD
returns.isLiquidatable: Whether the position can be liquidated

liquidateByDEX(address,uint256).details: Anyone can call this function to liquidate unhealthy positions

params.borrower: The address of the borrower to liquidate
params.liquidationIncentive: The liquidation incentive in basis points (e.g., 500 = 5%)

returns.liquidatedAmount: Amount of debt repaid through liquidation

liquidateByMEV(address,uint256,uint256).details: Liquidator pays debt and receives collateral with incentive

params.borrower: The address of the borrower to liquidate
params.liquidationIncentive: The liquidation incentive in basis points
params.repayAmount: Amount of debt the liquidator wants to repay

repayWithSelectedToken(uint256,address,b.custom:throws: ZeroAmount if shares is 0.amountSharesInvalid if shares exceed user's borrow shares.
repayWithSelectedToken(uint256,address,b.details: Swaps selected token to borrow token if needed via position contract. Accrues interest before repayment.

params._fromPosition: Whether to use tokens from the position contract (true) or from the user's wallet (false).
params._token: The address of the token to use for repayment.
params.shares: The number of borrow shares to repay.

supplyCollateral(uint256,address).details: Transfers collateral tokens from user to their Position contract. Accrues interest before deposit.

params._amount: The amount of collateral tokens to supply.
params._user: The address of the user to supply collateral.

supplyLiquidity(address,uint256).details: Users receive shares proportional to their deposit. Shares represent ownership in the pool. Accrues interest before deposit.

params._amount: The amount of borrow tokens to supply as liquidity.
params._user: The address of the user to supply liquidity.

withdrawCollateral(uint256).custom:throws: ZeroAmount if amount is 0.InsufficientCollateral if user has insufficient collateral balance.
withdrawCollateral(uint256).details: Transfers collateral tokens from Position contract back to user. Accrues interest before withdrawal.

params._amount: The amount of collateral tokens to withdraw.

withdrawLiquidity(uint256).custom:throws: ZeroAmount if _shares is 0.InsufficientShares if user does not have enough shares.InsufficientLiquidity if protocol lacks liquidity after withdrawal.
withdrawLiquidity(uint256).details: Calculates the corresponding asset amount based on the proportion of total shares. Accrues interest before withdrawal.

params._shares: The number of supply shares to redeem for underlying tokens.

borrowDebt(uint256,uint256,uint32,uint12.notice: Borrow assets using supplied collateral and optionally send them to a different network.

checkLiquidation(address).notice: Checks if a borrower's position is liquidatable

liquidateByDEX(address,uint256).notice: Liquidates an unhealthy position using DEX swapping

liquidateByMEV(address,uint256,uint256).notice: Liquidates an unhealthy position by allowing MEV/external liquidator to buy collateral

repayWithSelectedToken(uint256,address,b.notice: Repay borrowed assets using a selected token from the user's position.

supplyCollateral(uint256,address).notice: Supply collateral tokens to the user's position in the lending pool.

supplyLiquidity(address,uint256).notice: Supply liquidity to the lending pool by depositing borrow tokens.

withdrawCollateral(uint256).notice: Withdraw supplied collateral from the user's position.

withdrawLiquidity(uint256).notice: Withdraw supplied liquidity by redeeming shares for underlying tokens.
